<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11199</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>19120</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我饿了。”八戒抱怨道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>19121</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>22654</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他的肚子咕咕叫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>22655</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>25392</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们能休息一会儿吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>25393</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>29654</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们很快就可以吃午饭了。”唐僧说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>29655</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>32728</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“天气很好，道路也很平。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>32729</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>36714</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我想继续走，希望能早点儿到达西天。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>36715</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>42272</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空大笑。“师父，你为什么还要去西天？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>42273</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>45426</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你应该和那个蝎子精结婚的！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>45427</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>48393</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧皱起了眉头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>48394</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>50534</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这不好笑，悟空。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>50535</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>53250</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我同意。”八戒说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>53251</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>57262</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“如果是我，我会很高兴和她结婚的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>57263</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>60599</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟净扬起了一边的眉毛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>60600</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>63732</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我怀疑她想不想和你结婚。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>63733</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>69654</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“为什么不想？”八戒挺起了胸膛。“我很帅啊！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>69655</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>74416</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大家都大笑起来，连八戒自己都笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>74417</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>77757</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们又走了一个小时。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>77758</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>80326</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒又开始抱怨了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>80327</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>84295</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我的腿好疼。”他说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>84296</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>88483</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们在下一个村子休息吧。”唐僧说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>88484</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>95359</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒叹气。“希望我们很快就能到下一个村子。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>95360</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>99360</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我有个好办法。”悟空笑着说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>99361</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>102259</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空用力打了一下马。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>102260</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>105223</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那马迅速向前跑去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>105224</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>111982</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“悟空！”唐僧紧紧抓着缰绳大叫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>111983</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>119264</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>马停下的时候，唐僧已经跑出很远了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>119265</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>124846</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>几个长得很凶的人站在他面前。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>124847</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>130175</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“把你的钱都交出来！”一个拿着斧头的男人说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>130176</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>133509</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧吓得浑身发抖。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>133510</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>136803</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这时，悟空跑了过来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>136804</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>142907</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谁敢伤害我师父！”悟空大叫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>142908</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>146591</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你是谁？”男人问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>146592</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>150244</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我是孙悟空。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>150245</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>155499</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“把你的钱交出来。”男人说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>155500</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>158386</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我没有钱。”悟空说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>158387</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>161098</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们还是把钱给我吧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>161099</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>164163</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>男人的脸气得涨红了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>164164</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>166665</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我才不会给你钱呢！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>166666</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>170164</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那我们来打个赌吧。”悟空说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>170165</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>171990</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他抽出了金箍棒。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>171991</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>176324</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>金箍棒迅速变长，有一个人那么高。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>176325</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>179731</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那个男人看上去很紧张。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>179732</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>183123</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空把金箍棒立在了地上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>183124</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>187749</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“如果你能把这个抬起来，我们就把钱给你。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>187750</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>191657</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“傻瓜。”拿着斧头的男人说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>191658</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>194962</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我肯定能抬起那根棒子的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>194963</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>198265</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那你就试试。”悟空说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>198266</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>201179</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那个男人放下了斧头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>201180</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>207064</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他双手抓住了金箍棒，努力想把它抬起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>207065</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>212372</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这棒子比看上去的要重啊。”男人说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>212373</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>214782</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他又试着抬了一下。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>214783</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>219357</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他的脸涨得通红，汗珠不停地滑落，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>219358</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>222803</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但金箍棒依然动都没动。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>222804</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>226524</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在，轮到我了。”悟空说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>226525</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>231758</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他把金箍棒举过了头顶，不停地旋转。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>231759</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>233986</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他的眼睛冒着怒火。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>233987</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>237862</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他已经准备好要打那个男人了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>237863</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>242839</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“悟空，不要！”唐僧大叫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>242840</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>245384</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那个男人退后了一步。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>245385</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>249796</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，金箍棒从悟空的手里掉了下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>249797</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>254174</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊！”悟空抱着头大叫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>254175</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>257527</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧默默地念起了紧箍咒。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>257528</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>260795</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空痛得跪在地上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>260796</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>264986</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>强盗们互相看了看，逃走了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>264987</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>267316</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧停止了念咒。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>267317</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>269444</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空很生气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>269445</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>276969</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你为什么要这么做？”他大叫，“他们要......”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>276970</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>280349</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你不能伤人！”唐僧说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>69</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>280350</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>285518</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我一路上都在打妖怪。”悟空说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>70</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>285519</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>291971</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“打妖怪可以，但你不能伤人。”唐僧叹了口气，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>71</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>291972</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>295310</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你还是那么暴力，悟空。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>72</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>295311</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>301596</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我不能带你去西天。你走吧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>73</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>301597</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>310714</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是，你需要我啊，师父！”悟空坚持说，“我不走。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>74</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>310715</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>315945</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“走！”唐僧说，“不然，我就念紧箍咒了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>75</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>315946</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>319709</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我会一直念到你脑袋爆炸的！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>76</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>319710</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>333731</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空看到唐僧主意已定，含泪跳到空中离开了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>